Question: One image shows a yellow-cabbed truck with its plow at an angle that makes it look sharply curved and concave.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: http://wtop.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/IMG_5478.jpg

Right image URL: https://bdn-data.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2010/09/1283601116_6f9a-1024x664.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image show a yellow-cabbed truck?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image show a yellow-cabbed truck?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the plow at an angle that makes it look sharply curved and concave?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the plow at an angle that makes it look sharply curved and concave?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
